casebody.data:
Beth KELLER
v.
Richard KELLER Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided June 21, 2017 Nadine M. Pare, in support of the petition. Richard A. Keller, self-represented, in opposition.

The plaintiffs petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court (AC 39842) is denied.

ROGERS, C. J., did not participate in the consideration of or decision on this petition.
